<< /Length 964 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (VISUAL MORNING ROUTINE CHART) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (\(Laminate and hang in bedroom/bathroom!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (MORNING ROUTINE \(Do in this order!\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (  [1] [ ] Wake up - sit up in bed!) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (  [2] [ ] Use the bathroom) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (  [3] [ ] Brush teeth \(timer: 2 min\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (  [4] [ ] Get dressed \(clothes laid out last night!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.2 Td (  [5] [ ] Eat breakfast) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.2 Td (  [6] [ ] Pack backpack \(check list!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.2 Td (  [7] [ ] Shoes on, ready to go!) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.2 Td (  [8] [ ] OUT THE DOOR by ___:___ AM) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.4 Td (PARENT TIP: Let child check off steps themselves. Each checkmark = dopamine!) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.4 Td (BONUS: If all done by ___:___, earn ____________________!) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
