BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.2 Td (  [8] [ ] Evening routine \(below\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 558.4 Td (KEY: Movement BEFORE homework. A tired ADHD brain cannot focus!) Tj ET
