stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (ADHD-FRIENDLY REWARD SYSTEM) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (ADHD brains need EXTERNAL motivation. This isn't bribery - it's brain science!) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 662.2 Td (TOKEN BOARD \(earn tokens, trade for rewards\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (EARN TOKENS FOR:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (  * Routine completed \(morning/afternoon/bedtime\) = 1 token) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.2 Td (  * Homework done without major battle = 2 tokens) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.2 Td (  * Kind to siblings = 1 token) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.2 Td (  * Tried something hard = 1 token) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.2 Td (  * Remembered something without reminding = 2 tokens!) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.4 Td (SPEND TOKENS ON:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.4 Td (  5 tokens = Extra screen time \(30 min\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.4 Td (  10 tokens = Choose dinner / Pick a movie) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 510.4 Td (  15 tokens = Special outing with parent) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 496.4 Td (  20 tokens = New book/toy \(under $10\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 482.4 Td (  30 tokens = BIG reward: _______________) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 458.6 Td (TOKENS EARNED: [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ]) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.6 Td (               [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ] [  ]) Tj ET
endstream
