stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (HOMEWORK STATION SETUP GUIDE) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Create a distraction-free zone that works WITH ADHD:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (LOCATION: [ ] Desk in room [ ] Kitchen table [ ] Quiet corner) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (\(Wherever YOU can supervise without hovering\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 624.4 Td (STATION MUST HAVES:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.4 Td (  [ ] Timer \(visual timer best - they can SEE time passing\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.4 Td (  [ ] Fidget tool \(quiet one: putty, stress ball, tangle\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.4 Td (  [ ] Noise-canceling headphones OR white noise) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.4 Td (  [ ] All supplies within reach \(pencils, eraser, sharpener\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.4 Td (  [ ] Water bottle \(hydration helps focus!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.4 Td (  [ ] Clear desk surface \(nothing extra - only current task\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.4 Td (  [ ] Checklist of assignments \(visible, checkable\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 500.6 Td (HOMEWORK STRATEGY: 10 min work -> 3 min break -> 10 min work -> 3 min break) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.6 Td (\(Adjust times to your child: some do better with 15/5, some need 7/3\)) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
