BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SENSORY BREAK MENU) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (When your child is dysregulated, overwhelmed, or can't focus - offer a SENSORY BREAK:) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 662.2 Td (HIGH ENERGY \(burn it off\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (  [ ] Jump on trampoline) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (  [ ] Run laps around house) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.2 Td (  [ ] Dance to one song) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.2 Td (  [ ] 10 jumping jacks) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.2 Td (  [ ] Push-ups against wall) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 572.2 Td (CALMING \(settle down\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.2 Td (  [ ] Deep pressure \(tight hug, weighted blanket\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.2 Td (  [ ] Swing or rock) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 528.2 Td (  [ ] Play with water/sand) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 514.2 Td (  [ ] Listen to calm music) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 500.2 Td (  [ ] Blow bubbles \(controlled breathing\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 482.2 Td (FOCUSING \(get ready to work\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 466.2 Td (  [ ] Chew gum or crunchy snack) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 452.2 Td (  [ ] Fidget tool) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 438.2 Td (  [ ] Cold water on wrists) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 424.2 Td (  [ ] Stretching) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 410.2 Td (  [ ] 5 deep breaths) Tj ET
endstream
